WEBVTT

00:01.540 --> 00:08.050
The advantage to using Google Apps for business sometimes can actually be a disadvantage.

00:08.050 --> 00:09.270
Let me explain that.

00:09.430 --> 00:15.480
We work on servers the Google servers the servers are in the cloud the cloud rains down on us anywhere

00:15.490 --> 00:19.390
we are that has a wireless connection and we can work anywhere we want.

00:19.390 --> 00:21.200
We can communicate with our coworkers.

00:21.280 --> 00:25.070
We can send them stuff spreadsheets whatever.

00:25.090 --> 00:27.030
That is the advantage.

00:27.070 --> 00:33.100
The disadvantage is in my opinion what if you want to work on something but you don't have a connection

00:33.100 --> 00:38.650
to the Google servers if you're on an airplane and you don't want to spend the extra money for the new

00:38.830 --> 00:40.250
wireless service.

00:40.420 --> 00:41.830
And I don't blame you.

00:41.900 --> 00:44.180
Maybe you're going to be on the airplane for an hour or two.

00:44.260 --> 00:47.790
You just want to catch up on a document if you're off line.

00:47.830 --> 00:50.840
You can view stuff but you can't change it.

00:50.870 --> 00:54.520
Let me show you something if we go into more right here.

00:54.520 --> 00:57.970
Now this will be in any one of the Google Apps.

00:57.970 --> 01:00.570
There is an option for off line.

01:00.580 --> 01:06.190
Now we have already installed the drive but if I go to off line it'll tell me I already have the web

01:06.190 --> 01:06.910
app.

01:06.910 --> 01:15.980
Basically what this does is it puts editable copies of my documents on my computer and if I enable offline

01:16.000 --> 01:16.930
that's what it will do.

01:16.930 --> 01:20.030
So you have to be online now to get it done.

01:20.140 --> 01:26.080
But the process then goes this way I can say get on the airplane or whatever I can do any work that

01:26.080 --> 01:32.760
I want to and when I get back online the updates will be transferred to the Google servers.

01:32.770 --> 01:40.870
So the advantage of having Google business which is good can also be a disadvantage but not if you enable

01:41.110 --> 01:42.570
off line editing.

01:42.640 --> 01:44.040
It's as easy as that.
